COMMAND_GROUPS = """Command groups:
  skill: skill doctor, skill install, skill update, skill pack
  agent runner: configure-agent, doctor-agent
  planning: init, write-brief, plan, audit-plan, revise-plan, activate-plan
  execution: start, run, preview, tick, pause, resume, stop, attach, status, health, validate, reconcile, summarize, logs, rebuild-read-models, final-verify, migrate
  background: background start, background status, background complete, background cancel
  migration: export --profile source|stateful|archive --output <archive>, import <archive> --target <project>
  dashboard: dashboard, dashboard list, dashboard cleanup, dashboard stop
  template: template list, template show, template doctor, template render, template instance show, template extract-preset
  workspace: workspace current, workspace register, workspace unregister, workspace scan, workspace list, workspace doctor
  workflow: workflow list, workflow current, workflow show, workflow switch, workflow create, workflow archive, workflow restore, workflow fork
  inspection: ask, change-request, approvals, approve, reject
  version control: vc status, vc checkpoint, vc run-metadata, vc diff, vc log, vc rollback, vc export, vc import, vc doctor

Implemented commands call the standalone runtime. Commands outside the current
runtime implementation fail deterministically without claiming success.
"""

